        # Examples
        
        ## Set some dependency versions to new ones from a prior CI pipeline, and bump the major version (package.json)
        
        `update-version --set-dependencies react=1.2.3,react-dom=2.3.4 test/test-data/package1.json --bump major`
        
        ## Update the patch version in the .gitlab-ci.yml
        
        `update-version --bump patch test/test-data/.gitlab-ci.yml`
        
Platform: any
